metadata.dc:author: Vaccaro Cerva, H
metadata.dc:description: A fetal heart rhabdomyoma diagnosed at 31 weeks of gestational age, is presented. The tumor, located in the right ventricle, is asymptomatic. The diagnosis is confirmed postnatal.
metadata.dc:title: Diagnóstico prenatal de un rabdomioma cardíaco.
[Prenatal diagnosis of heart rhabdomyoma].
metadata.dc:publisher: Revista chilena de obstetricia y ginecologia
